\par \pard\plain \s6\sa120 \f2\fs20\lang1033 When the {\uldb pipe-command}{\v pipe_command} or the {\uldb filter-buffer}{\v filter_buffer} commands are used under Microsoft Windows, MicroEMACS creates a {\ul DOS box}{\v DosBox}
